    Scope and Contents
Papers of Clarence Danhof, Professor of Political Economy (1972-82) and Associate Dean of Organization and Management Studies (1979-82), including outgoing correspondence from Danhof to University faculty and administrators concerning administrative, curricular and student affairs.  

Also includes news clippings, publications budgets, maps, memoranda, and other collected research material concerning Danhof's research on Springfield's urban development, government and public services entitled Case Studies of Urban Government  
  
